headline: Nike, FedEx, Micron: Market Minute
summary: Yahoo Finance host Josh Lipton tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including Nike's (NKE) warning of tariff risks, FedEx (FDX) missing on fiscal third quarter earnings estimates, and Micron Technology's (MU) negative stock reaction to its latest earnings figures and guidance. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
